#. Tag: title
#: advanced-functions.docbook:8
#, no-c-format
msgid "Advanced functions"
msgstr "高级功能"

#. Tag: chapter
#: advanced-functions.docbook:8
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&vfs; &compare; &occupied-space; &splitter; &checksum; <sect1 id=\"send-"
"email\"> <title>Send Files by Email</title> <para>Select a file and use "
"<menuchoice> <guimenu>Right-Click menu</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Send by Email</"
"guimenuitem> </menuchoice>. Selecting this option will open a new &kmail; "
"window with the file already attached. Just fill in the subject and "
"recipient(s) and send it. Of course, &kmail; must be properly configured.</"
"para> </sect1> &profiles;"
msgstr ""
"&vfs; &compare; &occupied-space; &splitter; &checksum; <sect1 id=\"send-"
"email\"> <title>用电子邮件发送文件</title> <para>选择一个文件，然后用"
"<menuchoice> <guimenu>右键菜单</guimenu> <guimenuitem>通过电子邮件发送</"
"guimenuitem> </menuchoice>。此选项将打开一个新的 &kmail; 窗口，文件已经加入附"
"件。填写主题和收件人即可。当然 &kmail; 须经过适当配置。</para> </sect1> "
"&profiles;"

#. Tag: title
#: advanced-functions.docbook:34
#, no-c-format
msgid "ACL permissions"
msgstr "ACL 权限"

#. Tag: para
#: advanced-functions.docbook:35
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<link linkend=\"gloss-acl\">ACL permissions</link> are fully supported when "
"using properties, preserve attributes and the synchronizer. To view/modify "
"the ACL permissions, select a file and use the <link linkend=\"context-"
"menu\">Context Menu</link>: <menuchoice> <guimenu>Properties...</guimenu> "
"<guimenuitem>Permissions</guimenuitem> <guimenuitem>Advanced permissions</"
"guimenuitem> </menuchoice>. At Copy/Move, the ACL permissions are also "
"copied. The synchronizer keeps the ACL permissions as well."
msgstr ""
"使用属性、保留属性和同步器时，完全支持<link linkend=\"gloss-acl\">ACL 权限</"
"link> 。 要查看/修改 ACL 权限，请选择一个文件并使用 <link linkend=\"context-"
"menu\">上下文菜单</link>: <menuchoice> <guimenu>属性...</guimenu> "
"<guimenuitem>权限</guimenuitem> <guimenuitem>高级权限</guimenuitem> </"
"menuchoice>在复制/移动时，ACL权限也被复制。同步器也保留ACL权限。"
